# 🎯 11. `this` Keyword 🔥🔥

---

## Normal Function

```js
let obj = {
  name: "Lucky",
  greet() {
    console.log(this.name);
  }
};
```

✔ `this` = object

---

## Arrow Function

```js
let obj = {
  name: "Lucky",
  greet: () => {
    console.log(this.name);
  }
};
```

❌ `this` NOT object

---

# 🎯 12. `call()`, `apply()`, `bind()` ⭐

---

## 🔹 call()

```js
function greet() {
  console.log(this.name);
}

greet.call({name: "Lucky"});
```

---

## 🔹 apply()

```js
